author: Danica Kirka / AP
title: Another U.K. Cabinet Member Has Developed COVID-19 Symptoms
description: Another member of British Prime Minister Boris Johnson’s Cabinet has symptoms of COVID-19, as the nation surpassed 1,000 coronavirus deaths.
content:
(LONDON) — Another member of British Prime Minister Boris Johnson’s Cabinet has developed symptoms of COVID-19, as the number of people with the coronovrius to die in the U.K. passed the 1,000 mark Saturday.
